com.pb.sawdust.tabledata.transform.row

Class BasicDataRowsRemoval

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pb.sawdust.tabledata.transform.row.DataRowsRemoval<DataRow>
      • com.pb.sawdust.tabledata.transform.row.BasicDataRowsRemoval
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataTableTransformation, MutatingDataTableTransformation

    public class BasicDataRowsRemoval
extends DataRowsRemoval<DataRow>
    The BasicDataRowsRemoval is a row-removal data table transformation which only uses the row's data to determine if it should be removed or not. That is, it is a non-contextual row-removal transformation.
